@startuml

title Section 18.3 - Iteration 3 Event-Driven Workflow
left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

component "Order Orchestrator" as orchestrator
component "Payment Service" as payment
component "Shipping Service" as shipping
component "Notification Service" as notification
queue "RabbitMQ Event Bus" as bus

orchestrator --> bus : publish OrderCreated
bus --> payment : consume OrderCreated
payment --> bus : publish PaymentSucceeded | PaymentFailed
bus --> shipping : consume PaymentSucceeded
shipping --> bus : publish ShipmentCreated
bus --> notification : consume workflow events

note right of orchestrator
Compensation logic can react to
PaymentFailed or ShipmentFailed.
end note

@enduml
